  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this research is to compare a novel pelvic MetaWear sensor that looks at spine&#xD;
      and pelvic movements when taking lateral sit-to-stand radiographs.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
